       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ZZZ816.
       AUTHOR. SID WAITE.
       DATE-COMPILED. TODAY.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT PAYCUR ASSIGN TO "S30" ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
           ACCESS MODE IS DYNAMIC RECORD KEY IS PAYCUR-KEY.
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD PAYCUR
           BLOCK CONTAINS 6 RECORDS
           DATA RECORD IS PAYCUR01.
       01 PAYCUR01.
           02 PAYCUR-KEY.
             03 PC-KEY8 PIC X(8).
             03 PC-KEY3 PIC XXX.
           02 PC-AMOUNT PIC S9(4)V99.
           02 PC-PAYCODE PIC 999.
           02 PC-DENIAL PIC XX.
           02 PC-CLAIM PIC X(6).
           02 PC-DATE-T PIC X(8).
           02 PC-DATE-E PIC X(8).
           02 PC-BATCH PIC X(6).
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  CNTR PIC 9(4).
       01  HOLD8 PIC X(8).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       P0.
           OPEN I-O PAYCUR.
       P1. READ PAYCUR NEXT WITH LOCK AT END GO TO P2.
           IF PC-PAYCODE = "022" 
           MOVE "052" TO PC-PAYCODE
           REWRITE PAYCUR01.
           GO TO P1.
       P2. CLOSE PAYCUR. 
           STOP RUN.
